description:
**Drive traffic and sales**
List your products to grow awareness and drive both new and repeat sales, and let Tabby keep shoppers engaged with personalised recommendations and notifications.

**Access millions of power shoppers**
Millions of high-intent shoppers use Tabby Shop as their place for shopping inspiration. Make sure your products are listed to inspire them to purchase from your store.

**Track product performance**
See which items are sought-after and best-sellers so you can make informed decisions on procurement and pricing.

**Exclusively for Tabby retailers**
Not yet selling with Tabby? Sign up for Tabby Business to list your products in the Tabby app to drive traffic and sales.

**How to set up Tabby Catalogue**
1. Sign up with Tabby if you are not yet a Tabby retailer;
2. In the Zid App Market find the Tabby Catalogue App and install it in your store;
3. Click “Activate application” in the app page;
4. Wait to be redirected to the Tabby Merchant Dashboard;
5. Log in to the Dashboard/Create business profile;
6. At the Product Catalogue tab click 'Connect Zid';
7. Authorize your store;
8. Let your Zid store sync with your Tabby profile;
9. Check the processing and published items. Optionally, you can check any items that weren't processed and their errors to try to fix them;
10. Your products are now live on the Tabby app and shoppers can find your products when they browse Tabby Shop.

